727175f-b.text:
View No. 1 shows Laurel Hill Blvd. (car thereon) north from Newton Creek to Review Avenue.  In the background is seen a section of the Cavalry Cemetery.  Also shown is a branch spur of the Long Island Railroad (locomotive thereon).

View No. 2 shows a sectional view of the Creek and Fenny Bridge.

August 13, 1938.
Views 1 and 2

P.L. Sperr
